org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM versions INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = versions.project_id WHERE projects.id = 60 OR projects.status <> 9 AND (versions.sharing = 'system' OR projects.lft >= 13 AND projects.rgt <= 22 AND versions.sharing = 'tree' OR projects.lft < 17 AND projects.rgt > 18 AND versions.sharing IN ('hierarchy', 'descendants') OR projects.lft > 17 AND projects.rgt < 18 AND versions.sharing = 'hierarchy') LIMIT "$1"

rewrites.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM versions WHERE versions.sharing = 'system' OR versions.sharing = 'tree' OR versions.sharing IN ('hierarchy', 'descendants') OR versions.sharing = 'hierarchy' LIMIT "$1"
